    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Heitfolk are dwarven folk who inhabit Svellheim's geothermal zones — broad-shouldered, weathered warriors in thick cold-wrap leathers and chain hauberks, carrying axes and hammers forged in volcanic heat. They are not inherently hostile but are deeply protective of their sacred ground and geothermal sites. Heitfolk sentries cannot be flanked thanks to their Tunnel-Kin instincts, and in enclosed spaces they fight with exceptional precision and coordination.</p>",
